{"tid":843925,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每個人的人生 都在等待一個救世主","createTime":"2018-10-01T13:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:10:33.000Z","uid":181061,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13e79f074e481f91f5d974e74cde1facdf2ad4da","tid":843925,"uid":181061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"好記得當初，我好勇咁主動追妳<br />\n因為見到妳既孤單，想話妳知<br />\n妳可以有好有意義既人生<br />\n<br />\n妳大學，我Asso<br />\n妳Grad平步青雲<br />\n我Grad平淡到暈<br />\n但我主動拖起妳隻手<br />\n話妳知，我地不會卻步如此<br />\n<br />\n努力去諗，諗咗好多可以拉近我同妳距離既路<br />\n最後既決定，踏入我都唔知最後會點既路<br />\n但至少，我知道為咗我 地 既前路<br />\n跪低都要趴完依條路<br />\n而妳一直講既係<br />\n咩路都好，成唔成功都好，妳都會支持我，陪住我<br />\n<br />\n去到最後，我先岩岩起行<br />\n妳已經恨心離我而去<br />\n只知道感覺失了蹤？不知道戀愛這麼重？<br />\n花光了心血，還是不相信<br />\n<br />\n或者最後妳離開既原因<br />\n係妳口中所言<br />\n或者又係因為屋企人覺得我唔會成功而反對<br />\n但無論如何，妳都係走了<br />\n<br />\n然而我，或許沒有想象中的痛<br />\n至少曾經陪妳行過一程<br />\n至少我因妳，而挽起了很久的從前就埋藏在土壤既野心<br />\n至少妳，曾擔任我世界的救世主<br />\n<br />\n或許妳已經有一個更好既男仔<br />\n同妳行妳既餘生 附合妳同妳屋企人既要求<br />\n做你世界的救世主<br />\n<br />\n或是我、我們，都在各自等待自己人生的救世主<br />\n擔任別人的救世主，撫摸舊日的傷痕<br />\n再共渡餘生<br />\n<br />\n每個人的人生，都在等待一個救世主<br />\n或甦醒、或治癒、或同行<br />\n人生"},{"pid":"72bdb7469c65ef2a2499d5934e10200989065bd6","tid":843925,"uid":213894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"巴打堅強 你係一個好男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34290ba8827195383f1bbb8102640ad8abbb9c0d","tid":843925,"uid":33904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"好鬼老套 肉麻"},{"pid":"d2812789833fd382762036c15cf871787044a6ce","tid":843925,"uid":181061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72bdb7469c65ef2a2499d5934e10200989065bd6","tid":843925,"uid":213894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"巴打堅強 你係一個好男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"放低咗既傷痛先會開口講<br />\n等下一個更好既出現<br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f52e8dc583f001bdcf039bec797b96f50e4468","tid":843925,"uid":181061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"34290ba8827195383f1bbb8102640ad8abbb9c0d","tid":843925,"uid":33904,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"好鬼老套 肉麻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:37:18.000Z","msg":"世界就係咁<br />\n循環潮流同老套肉麻既交替<br />\n潮流既終點就係老套肉麻<br />\n老套肉麻既終點又係潮流"},{"pid":"36faf6cc3744fdc111bd67ad1a488998a13892ad","tid":843925,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔好咁傷心"},{"pid":"9ed2bf93183dff10417e41b389fb2bf2f0ed306e","tid":843925,"uid":181061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36faf6cc3744fdc111bd67ad1a488998a13892ad","tid":843925,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔好咁傷心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"過咗去喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3672d509611f7bb9e2e33336847b54b022657e","tid":843925,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed2bf93183dff10417e41b389fb2bf2f0ed306e","tid":843925,"uid":181061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36faf6cc3744fdc111bd67ad1a488998a13892ad","tid":843925,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"唔好咁傷心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"過咗去喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T13:44:21.000Z","msg":"每個人都會有被救贖嘅時候 只係可惜在你哋唔係互相救贖 下次輪到你去救贖第二個人啦"},{"pid":"2a97cbcb6c1d0eed1659a13b03dfc896915fdaaa","tid":843925,"uid":181061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea3672d509611f7bb9e2e33336847b54b022657e","tid":843925,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ed2bf93183dff10417e41b389fb2bf2f0ed